msgctxt "Talk_01"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Even with the <2.se_co>Divine Beast<3.re_co> out there\n"
"making a fuss, a little vai like you just\n"
"strolls into town...\n"
"You've done well to make it to\n"
"Gerudo Town.\n"
"\n"
"<4.so>The <5.se_co>chief<6.re_co> keeps saying that everything\n"
"is going to be OK, but thinking about the\n"
"<7.se_co>Divine Beast <8.re_co>makes me so uneasy...<9.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: set_colour (blue)
#. 5: reset_colour
#. 6: choice
msgctxt "Talk_02"
msgid ""
"<1.so>There's no guarantee that <2.se_co>Divine Beast<3.re_co>\n"
"won't come marching right into town.\n"
"\n"
"The <4.se_co>chief<5.re_co> keeps saying everything is\n"
"fine... But I can't help this anxious\n"
"feeling.<6.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: sound
#. 3: sound
msgctxt "Talk_03"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You crossed the Gerudo Desert to get\n"
"here, right? So you must have seen the\n"
"giant walking around outside...\n"
"<2.so>It appeared suddenly a few weeks ago.\n"
"It's a daunting sight.\n"
"\n"
"<3.so>If you get too close to it, it'll lash out at\n"
"you with lightning. I can't imagine what\n"
"would happen if it came to town..."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk_04"
msgid ""
"<1.so>You should be careful and not get too\n"
"close to it."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: sound
#. 5: set_colour (blue)
#. 6: reset_colour
msgctxt "Talk_05"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I know you. You're the one who came to\n"
"town when the <2.se_co>Divine Beast<3.re_co> was still\n"
"causing trouble, weren't you?\n"
"I remember thinking it was amazing that\n"
"a slender little Hylian had made it all the\n"
"way here in the midst of that.\n"
"But now it's calmed down, so it'll be\n"
"easier for tourists like you to come visit,\n"
"and the town will be even more lively.\n"
"<4.so>Still... There's no guarantee that the\n"
"<5.se_co>Divine Beast <6.re_co>won't act up again. Just\n"
"thinking about it makes me uneasy."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk_06"
msgid ""
"<1.so>This town is led by our fantastic chief,\n"
"Lady Riju. She became chief after her\n"
"mother, our old chief, passed away.\n"
"Though young, Lady Riju was our old\n"
"chief's only child, so naturally the duties\n"
"of leading the Gerudo fell to her."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: set_colour (blue)
#. 5: reset_colour
#. 6: choice
msgctxt "Talk_07"
msgid ""
"<1.so>There have been other troubles on top of\n"
"the <2.se_co>Divine Beast<3.re_co> acting violently.\n"
"\n"
"I hear it has the <4.se_co>chief<5.re_co> and her advisors\n"
"pretty worried...<6.ch>"
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
msgctxt "Talk_08"
msgid ""
"<1.so>Well... I'll just try to keep my spirits up.\n"
"Maybe visit the canteen then get a good\n"
"night's sleep..."
msgstr ""

