#. 3: reset_colour
msgctxt "Talk_12"
msgid ""
"<1.so>I don't know what caused it, but\n"
"I'm relieved to see that the <2.se_co>Divine Beast<3.re_co>\n"
"could be calmed!\n"
"I'm still uneasy, though... You never\n"
"know if it might start stomping around\n"
"again."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: set_colour (blue)
#. 3: reset_colour
#. 4: choice
msgctxt "Talk_13"
msgid ""
"<1.so>The <2.se_co>chief<3.re_co> says that thing used to be a\n"
"god who protected this area around\n"
"100 years ago...\n"
"But that story sounds too crazy to\n"
"believe, don't you think? I need to think\n"
"on it...<4.ch>"
msgstr ""

